Ku saurara: Daniel Sturridge na Liverpool ya zura kwallo a wasan da Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kashi a gasar Premier da Chelsea ta hanyar zura kwallo a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a Stamford Bridge a London.
Sturridge ya samu kwallon daga hannun Xherdan Shaqiri da ta kai sa'a 30 a raga a ragar Chelsea, inda suka ci 1-0.
Ya juya da ƙwallo zuwa gefen hagu kafin ya yi tafiya kusa da ƙofar gidan.
Sai ya yi nisa kuma ya shiga cikin tarun.
A takaice dai, kwallon ta wuce Kepa Arrizabalaga wanda ya yi tsalle zuwa cikin tsibirin.
"Kawai kana son shiga cikin wannan wuri, ka kasance a kan kari kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna fama da ci gaba, don haka ina fama da samun lokacin da zan iya", in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
"Na ga Kante yana zuwa ya tarbe ni amma ban kula da shi ba kuma na yi masa duka".
Chelsea ta ci gaba da ci 1-0 a lokacin da aka yi tazarce bayan da Eden Hazard na Belgium ya ci kwallo a minti na 25.
Mai kula da filin wasa mai suna Blue ya buga kwallo zuwa hannun Matthew Kovacic a filin wasa, kafin ya yi tsalle zuwa filin wasa na Liverpool.
Kovacic ya ci gaba da buga kwallon zuwa tsakiyar filin wasa.
Sai ya buga ƙwallo mai ƙarfi, ya jefa Hazard cikin kwari.
Hazard ya yi tsere daga gaban 'yan wasan gaba kuma ya ci gaba da buga wasan a saman raga da hagu ta hanyar Liverpool Alisson Becker.
Liverpool za ta fafata da Napoli a wasan rukuni na biyu na gasar zakarun Turai da za a yi a karfe uku na yammacin ranar Laraba a filin wasa na San Paolo da ke Naples, Italiya.
Chelsea za ta kara da Videoton a wasan UEFA Europa League da za a yi a ƙarfe uku na yammacin ranar Alhamis a birnin Landan.
