Wayde Sims harin: 'Yan sanda sun kama Dyteon Simpson wanda ake zargi da kisan shugaban LSU
'Yan sanda sun kama wani da ake zargi da laifin fyade da kisan Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwando na LSU mai shekara 20.
Dyteon Simpson, ɗan shekara 20, an tsare shi a kurkuku don kisan kai na biyu, in ji 'yan sanda a ofishin 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge
Jami'an 'yan sanda sun nuna bidiyon Sims da Simpson suna faɗa, kuma sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a lokacin faɗa.
'Yan sanda sun gano tabarau a wurin da aka yi ta'asar kuma sun ce an gano DNA na Simpson a cikin tabarau, in ji WAFB ga CBS.
Bayan sun yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda suka ce ya yarda cewa shi ne ya yi wa Sims mummunan rauni.
Advocate ya ce, an ba shi kyautar dala 350,000.
Ofishin mai binciken marasa lafiya na yankin East Baton Rouge ya ba da rahoto a ranar Jumma'a cewa dalilin mutuwar shi ne harbin bindiga da aka yi masa a kai da kuma wuyansa.
Ma'aikatar ta gode wa rundunar 'yan sanda ta jihar Louisiana, da 'yan sanda na jihar, da jami'an 'yan sanda na Jami'ar Southern da kuma al'ummar yankin da suka taimaka wajen kama mutumin.
Shugaban LSU Joe Alleva ya yaba wa majalisa don "ƙoƙarce -ƙoƙarcen da suke yi don neman adalci".
Sims yana ɗan shekara 20 ne kawai.
Yaron mai tsayi 6-foot-6 ya girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa, Wayne, ya taka leda a ƙungiyar ƙwallon ƙafa ta LSU.
Wannan dan wasan ya zira kwallaye 5.6 da kuma ceto 2.6 a wasan da ya buga a bara.
A safiyar ranar Jumma'a, kocin LSU Will Wade ya ce 'yan wasan sun yi "bacin rai" kuma sun "yi mamaki" da mutuwar Wayde.
Wade ya ce: "Wannan shi ne abin da kuke damuwa da shi".
Volcano yana haskaka duwatsu a birnin Mexico
