Masana ilimin ƙasa sun ce an sami ƙaruwa a aikin dutsen mai fitad da wuta da ke da nisan mil 45 (kilomita 72) daga arewacin babban birnin ƙasar tun lokacin da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.1 ta auku a tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumba, 2017.
