'Yan sanda sun yi arangama da 'yan Catalonia kafin bikin tunawa da zaben 'yancin kai
An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan da masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai suka yi arangama da 'yan sanda, yayin da wasu suka shiga zanga-zangar masu adawa da tsarin mulki a farkon bikin zaben raba gardama a Catalonia.
'Yan sanda da ke tsare da su sun yi amfani da wasu mutane da suka yi kama da ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma fenti don su yi musu bulala, suna yin turɓaya a kan titunan da ake son masu yawon bude ido su shiga.
An yi ta faɗa a wasu lokutan da rana kuma 'yan sanda sun yi amfani da sandunansu don su kawar da rikici.
A cikin sa'o'i da yawa masu son 'yancin kai suka yi ihu cewa "Ba za a manta da kome ba, ba za a gafarta wa kowa ba" yayin da 'yan Unionist suka yi ihu cewa "Ku ci gaba da zama 'yan Spain".
An yi wa mutane 14 jinya don raunuka kaɗan da suka ji a wannan harin, in ji kafofin yaɗa labarai na yankin.
Wannan abin tsoro ne a yankin 'yancin kai, shekara guda bayan an yi zaben raba gardama a ranar 1 ga watan Mayu, wanda aka yi wa la'anta a Madrid amma da aka yi bikin ne a Catalonia.
Yawancin masu jefa kuri'a sun yi zabe don samun 'yanci, ko da yake 'yan tsiraru ne kawai suka ƙi yin hakan.
A cewar hukumomin yankin Catalonia, mutane kusan 1,000 sun ji rauni a wannan shekarar bayan da 'yan sanda suka yi ƙoƙarin hana yin zabe a wani yanki da ke cike da rikici.
Ƙungiyoyin 'yanci sun kafa sansani a waje a ranar Jumma'a don su hana zanga-zangar goyon bayan 'yan sanda.
An ci gaba da zanga-zangar amma an tilasta musu su bi wata hanya dabam.
Wani mai aikin lantarki mai suna Narcis Termes, ɗan shekara 68, da matarsa da suka halarci zanga-zangar sun ce ba su da bege cewa Catalonia za ta samu 'yanci.
"Shekarar da ta shige ta kasance shekara ta salama.
Na ga iyayena suna kuka domin suna farin ciki cewa yanzu suna da 'yancin yin zaɓi amma yanzu an tilasta musu su yi hakan", in ji ta.
Duk da gagarumin nasarar da aka samu a zaben watan Disamba, 'yan adawar Catalonia na gwagwarmaya don samun iko a wannan shekara yayin da wasu daga cikin shugabanninsu ke cikin mafaka wasu kuma a kurkuku suna jiran hukunci saboda ayyukansu na shirya zaben raba gardama da kuma sanarwar 'yancin kai da ta biyo baya.
Joan Puig, mai shekara 42, mai gyara motoci da ke ɗaukan hotuna a waya da 'yan sanda ya ce 'yan siyasa a ɓangarorin biyu ne suke goyon bayan wannan zanga-zangar.
"Wannan magana tana da ban mamaki", in ji mutane.
A ranar Asabar, Oriol Junqueras, ɗaya daga cikin manyan shugabannin Catalonia guda tara da aka tsare a kurkuku ba tare da an yi musu shari'a ba a bara, ya sanar cewa zai tsaya takara a zaɓen Majalisar Turai na shekara mai zuwa.
"Matsayin da aka ba da a zaɓen Turai shi ne hanya mafi kyau na ƙin komawa ga tsarin mulkin kama karya da kuma mulkin kama karya da aka nuna a Spain", in ji shi.
