Lokacin taron Trump a West Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron zabensa na farko da yammacin yau a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ɗaya ne cikin taron taro guda biyar da Trump ya shirya a mako mai zuwa, har da wasu manyan shaguna a yankunan da ke da yawan jama'a da suka haɗa da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran tabbatar da kuri'un da za su tabbatar da cewa an zabi wani a Kotun Koli, Trump na son kara samun goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe a tsakiyar lokacin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar barazanar rasa ikon majalisar dokoki a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Shin lokacin da taron Trump na West Virginia ya fara ne a daren yau kuma ta yaya za ku fara shiga yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a West Virginia da karfe 7 na yamma ET yau da dare, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a YouTube ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye.
Ana sa ran Trump zai gabatar da jawabi a gaban kotun koli a wannan makon a kan zargin Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi tsanani saboda zargin da ake yi na kokarin gyara mace a lokacin da aka dage zaben tabbatar da gaskiya har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma, babban aikin da aka yi a waɗannan taron ya taimaka wa 'yan Republican su yi shiri sosai don zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A sakamakon haka, yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa Trump na biyar a wannan makon ya mayar da hankali ne kan "ba da damar masu goyon bayan Republican da ke son karewa da kuma kara yawan kujerun da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da na wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Majalisar ta matsa wa shugaban kasa ya yi tafiya sosai a lokacin da muke shiga wani lokaci na gaggawa na zaben", in ji wani kakakin kamfen na Trump wanda ya ƙi a ambaci shi a wata hira da Reuters.
An shirya taron na yau a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na iya jawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma manyan masu sauraro a tashoshin rediyo na Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, duk da cewa ta samu kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada a zaben 2016.
Trump yana ƙoƙarin ya taimaki dan majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya kasance a cikin wannan zaɓen.
"Har ila, Morrisey ba ya nuna cewa shugaban kasa ya kamata ya zo ya taimaka wajen ƙara yawan kuri'un da aka kada", in ji Simon Haeder, wani farfesa a jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
