Charles Czeisler, wani masanin maganin barci a Harvard Medical School kuma wani likita a Brigham and Women's Hospital, ya yi wannan binciken da ya ce shi ne na farko a ƙasar Amirka.
An ƙarfafa su su soma nazarin bayan sun tattauna yadda rashin barci yake shafan yadda suke yin nazari.
'A ƙarshen jawabin, wata yarinya ta zo ta ce: 'Me ya sa aka gaya mini waɗannan abubuwa a ƙarshen shekara ta farko na makarantar sakandare?'
