Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar ɗan adam a Makarantar Koyar da Lafiya ta Harvard kuma shugaban sashen kiwon lafiya a makarantar, ya ce makarantar ta zaɓi wannan binciken ne bayan da ta lura cewa ɗalibai suna rashin barci a cikin mako.
Wannan nazari na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da ayyuka da yawa na tattaunawa.
A cikin wani labarin akwai hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibai ke kwance a kan kofi, littattafai da littattafai don a gaya musu yadda kofi da haske ke aiki da kuma yadda rashin barci da rashin barci ke shafar aiki.
A wani talifi kuma, an koya wa ɗalibai cewa rashin barci na dogon lokaci yana daɗa haɗarin ciwon zuciya, shanyewar jiki, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar makaranta da kuma hotuna da ake amfani da su wajen tattaunawa suna ƙarfafa ɗalibai su yi tunani a kan abin da suke yi a kowace rana.
