HIV/Aids: China ta ce yawan sabbin kamuwa da cutar ya kai kashi 14 cikin 100
China ta ba da rahoton cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya ƙaru da kashi 14 cikin ɗari.
Mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suke fama da wannan cutar a dukan duniya, in ji wani babban jami'in kiwon lafiya.
An samu sabon adadin mutane 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kaɗai.
Mutane da yawa da aka ambata a baya sun kamu da cutar ta wajen yin lalata da su.
A dā, yawancin mutane da ke da cutar HIV a ƙasar Sin suna kamuwa da ita ta hanyar jini.
Amma adadin kamuwa da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar ya kusan ƙarewa, in ji ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Amma idan aka gwada da shekarun baya, adadin mutane da ke da cutar HIV da Aids a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da fiye da 100,000.
Yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babban lamari ne a kasar Sin da ke da yawan mutanen da ke da jima'i da ke cikin jima'i da ke cikin jima'i da ke cikin jima'i (LGBT).
A shekara ta 1997, an kawar da cin zarafin jinsi ɗaya a ƙasar Sin, amma an ce ana tsananta wa mutanen da suke yin lalata da juna.
Domin yanayin duniya da ke ɗaukaka al'adu da kuma al'adu, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90 cikin ɗari na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza sun daina yin jima'i da mata.
Yawancin cututtuka masu tsanani suna faruwa ne domin rashin kāriya a wannan hanyar.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin ƙasar Sin ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta yi wa dukan 'yan ƙasar riga-kafi don kawar da cutar HIV.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wata sanarwa da ta fito daga 'yan majalisa ta 'yan jam'iyyar Republican' ta yada 'ƙarya mai haɗari' da kuma 'labarin da ke nuna shakku'
A ranar Asabar ne wakilin majalisar wakilai na Amurka, Maxine Waters, ta yi watsi da zargin cewa wani daga cikin ma'aikatanta ya sanya bayanan wasu sanatoci uku na Republican a shafinsa na Wikipedia.
Dan Democrat na Los Angeles ya ce "masu fafutukar dama" ne suka yi amfani da wannan ra'ayi da kuma shafukan yanar gizo.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya, ƙaramar ƙarya", in ji Waters a shafinsa na Twitter.
An ba da rahoton cewa jawabin da aka watsa ya ƙunshi lambobin gida da kuma lambobin waya na Sanata Lindsey Graham na Amirka daga South Carolina, Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka daga Utah.
Wannan labarin ya bayyana ne a shafin yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani wanda ba a san ko shi wane ne ba ya bayyana a kan Capitol Hill a yayin da ake sauraron shari'ar da majalisar dattijai ta yi game da zargin da ake yi na neman gyara wa sabon shugaban kotun kolin kasar Brett Kavanaugh.
Labarin ya bazu ne bayan da sanatoci uku suka kammala shari'ar Kavanaugh.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ce adireshin IP da ke nuna mai aikawa ya haɗu da ofishin Waters kuma ya ba da labarin ma'aikacin Waters, in ji Hill.
"Wannan zato da ba a tabbatar da shi ba ƙarya ce mai tsanani da kuma ɓarna", in ji Waters.
"Bawana, wanda kuka yi masa alama, da maganganu, da sihiri, da ruɗu, da faɗar ƙarya, ba ya faɗa gaskiya.
"Wannan zato ne marar tushe, ƙarya ce mai tsanani da kuma ɓatanci.
Waters ya yi saurin samun karbuwa a shafukan intanet, ciki har da wani mai ba da rahoto a fadar White House, Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda da mugun abu ne", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba shi da zuciyarsa na zama memba na Majalisar.
Idan aka zargi mutum da yin abin da bai dace ba, bai kamata ya yi fushi ba.
Bai kamata ya yi fushi don ya kāre kansa ba.
Bai kamata ya tambayi wanda ya tuhume shi dalilin da ya sa ya yi hakan ba.
Amma ya kamata ya kasance da tawali'u da haƙuri".
Fleischer yana ƙoƙari ya kwatanta fushin Waters da na 'yan Democrat game da Alkalin Kavanaugh, wanda masu tuhuma suka ce ya yi fushi sosai a lokacin shari'ar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, wanda ya tsaya a kan takarar Republican don kawar da Waters a zaben tsakiyar lokaci, ya yi tsokaci a shafin Twitter.
"Wannan ya fi muhimmanci idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi a shafin Twitter.
A cikin wata sanarwa, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya tuntubi "duka masu ruwa da tsaki da kuma hukumomin tsaro game da wannan zargin da ake yi.
"Za mu tabbata cewa an kama masu laifi", in ji shi, "kuma za a tuhume su don ayyukansu na halaka da kuma haɗari ga kowa da kuma ma'aikatansa".
Johnny English ya sake dawowa - Rowan Atkinson ya gwada wasan kwaikwayo
Yanzu ya zama al'ada don raba abubuwan da suka faru da Brexit a cikin sabon tarihin tarihin Burtaniya da abin da ke faruwa a cikin sabon wasan kwaikwayo mai ban dariya mai ban dariya mai suna Johnny English action-comedy spoof franchise - wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake dawowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
Zai iya kawo zargi mai daɗi game da matsalarmu a matsayinmu na ƙasa game da yadda za mu iya fitar da kayayyakinmu?
Ko yaya dai, Johnny English mai idanu masu haske, da fuska mai sauƙi ya ɗauki takardar shaidarsa ta biyu ta zama mai wasan kwaikwayo - suna da ya nuna cewa ya ba da kansa sosai ga aikin wasan kwaikwayo na baƙi.
Wani mutum mai amfani da wani abu mai ban dariya wanda zai iya ba da damar yin wasa da shi a matsayin ɗan ɗan kallo, yana kwaikwayon Mr Bean da kuma wani nau'i na irin wannan mutumin da ke ƙara murya ga Chariots of Fire a bikin bude gasar Olympics ta London 2012.
Da farko kuma, ya dogara ga Atkinson, wani mai tafiya mai nisa da kuma duniya, wanda ya shiga cikin wani gidan rediyo da ake manta da shi yanzu, wanda ke ɗauke da takardar sanarwa ta Barclaycard TV, wanda ya hana shi fuskantar matsaloli a duk inda ya je.
Akwai abubuwa biyu ko fiye masu kyau da ke cikin sabon tsarin JE.
Na yi farin cikin ganin Johnny English yana zuwa jirgi mai saukar ungulu a cikin tsohuwar rigar soja da kuma fuka-fukan da ke kan gaba.
Kyautar Atkinson ta wasan kwaikwayo tana bayyane, amma a wasu lokuta wasan kwaikwayo yana da ɗan gajeren lokaci kuma yana da ɗan lokaci, musamman ma lokacin da aka kwatanta da abubuwan da ke faruwa a yanzu kamar 007 da Mission Impossible
Abin da ya fi dacewa shi ne cewa wasan kwaikwayon ya fi dacewa da matasa fiye da manya, kuma a yawancin lokuta Johnny English ba shi da wani abu mai kyau kamar yadda yake a cikin wasan kwaikwayon Atkinson a matsayin Bean.
A wannan shekara, ana ba da jawabi a kan batun nan: "Great Britain in Trouble".
Wani dan jarida mai amfani da Intane ya shiga cikin asirin intanet na 'yan leƙen asirin Birtaniya, ya fallasa dukan bayanan da ke cikin asusun 'yan leƙen asirin Birtaniya, abin mamaki ga wanda ke aiki a lokacin - aikin da Kevin Eldon bai yi ba.
Wannan abu ne mai wuya ga firaminista mai girman kai da kuma wahala, wanda ke fama da rashin iko da kuma rashin amincewa da siyasa: Emma Thompson tana da kyau a matsayin mai suna Theresa May amma ba ta da yawa a cikin jerin sunayen da za su yi aiki.
An umurci masu kula da aikin su yi wa waɗanda suka daina aiki aiki a lokacin da aka daina yin aikin.
Wannan ya haɗa da Johnny English, wanda yanzu shi ne shugaban makarantar, yana ba da shawarwari game da yadda za a yi aiki a ɓoye: abin ban dariya, a lokacin da English yake koyar da ilimin sihiri a School of Rock.
An kai English Whitehall don taron farko kuma ya sake saduwa da tsohon abokinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya yi.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, kuma an sanya shi tare da kyaftin na farko, wata mace mai suna Vicki Pepperdine wanda ya kasance mai ban sha'awa.
Saboda haka, abubuwa da ba za a iya kawar da su ba a cikin Asirin Sarauniya sun sake komawa kuma ya sadu da Ophelia Bulletova, wadda ta dace da Olga Kurylenko.
A wani ɓangare kuma, firaministan ƙasar ya faɗa cikin tarkon wani mai arziki mai kula da dabbobi da ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalar dabbobi a ƙasar Biritaniya: Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya yi.
Sai English da Bough suka soma wani irin tafiya na kama-da-wane: suna yin kamar su masu ba da abinci ne, suna nunawa a cikin wani babban gidan abinci na Faransa; suna kawo ƙwari a lokacin da suke tserewa a cikin jirgin ruwa mai daraja na Volta; kuma English yana kawo ƙwari lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin yin amfani da na'urar sauraro ta Virtual Reality don ganin yadda aka gina gidan Volta.
An cire duk abin da ke wakiltar wannan don a yi kallon ƙarshe, amma ko da yake yana da kyau kuma yana da ban sha'awa a wannan hanyar, har yanzu akwai abubuwan da ke da alaƙa da yara a cikin labarin.
Abubuwa da suka dace.
Kuma kamar yadda yawancin fina-finan Johnny English suke, na yi tunani: Shin ba za a iya ba wa Rowan Atkinson rawar da za ta sa ta yi amfani da basirarta ba?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta ki amincewa da dokar da ta ce 'yan Birtaniya su riƙa yin aiki kwana huɗu a mako kuma su riƙa samun albashi na kwana biyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn tana tunanin wani tsari da zai sa 'yan Britaniya su yi aiki na kwana huɗu a mako - a maimakon haka, su sami albashi na kwana biyar.
An ce an ce an yi wannan shirin ne don a ba shugabannin kamfanoni damar ba ma'aikata ƙarin hutu a kan kuɗin da aka samu daga aikin da aka yi da fasaha.
Hakan zai ba ma'aikata hutu na kwana uku a ƙarshen mako - amma a daidai albashi.
Masu ba da jawabi sun ce waɗannan shirye-shiryen za su "dace" a tattalin arziki da kuma a duniya don kyautata rayuwar ma'aikata.
Ma'aikata da yawa sun amince da wannan canjin da aka yi a matsayin hanyar samun sauƙi a lokacin da ake fuskantar matsalar tattalin arziki.
Wani shugaban jam'iyyar Labour ya gaya wa jaridar Sunday Times: 'Ana sa ran za a sanar da wannan gyara kafin ƙarshen shekara.
'Ba za a yi aiki na kwanaki huɗu ba, amma za a yi aiki na kwanaki huɗu a mako guda, wanda zai daidaita tsarin gwamnati na inganta rayuwar ma'aikata da kuma tsarin tattalin arziki na duniya.'
Jam'iyyar Labour ba za ta fara cimma wannan burin ba, yayin da Jam'iyyar Green ta yi alkawarin ranar aiki ta kwana hudu a lokacin zaben shugaban kasa na 2017.
Amma, jam'iyyar Labour ba ta amince da wannan shawarar ba.
Wani kakakin Jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: 'Mako na kwana huɗu ba wata manufa ba ce kuma ba a taɓa yin tunani a kai ba.'
John McDonnell, wanda shi ne Shugaban Ruwa, ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour na wannan makon don ya sake bayyana ra'ayinsa na inganta tattalin arziki da kasuwanci.
McDonnell ya ce yana da himma wajen kwace iko daga "shugabannin da ba su da wata manufa" da kuma "masu son cin gajiyar" kamfanonin da ke ba da sabis na ƙasa.
Shirin ya zama mai ba da shawara kuma yana nufin cewa masu hannun jari na kamfanonin ruwa ba za su iya samun cikakken kuɗin da suka samu ba saboda gwamnatin Labour za ta "ba da" wasu kudade don wasu laifuffuka.
Sun kuma amince da shirin koyar da ma'aikata a cikin ƙungiyoyi da kuma kafa asusun mallakar mallaka na musamman da zai ba da kashi 10 cikin ɗari na kuɗin equity ga ma'aikata, waɗanda za su iya samun albashi na shekara-shekara har zuwa £500.
