Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro dandalin Intane na Duniya, ya yi wani sabon tsarin da zai yi nasara da Facebook da Amazon da kuma Google.
Wani sabon bincike da wannan masanin ya yi ya nuna cewa wani sabon kamfani mai suna Inrupt yana aiki a kan wani sabon tsarin bincike na Berners-Lee mai suna Solid.
Shafin Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana labarinsu da kuma wanda za a duba labarin da kuma lokacin da za a duba shi.
A wata hira da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ba'a cewa ainihin manufar Inrupt ita ce "ta'allaka duniya".
