A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya kawo canji a tsarin yanar gizo sa'ad da ya kafa cibiyar sadarwa ta duniya, wato, World Wide Web Consortium a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watanni da suka shige, Berners-Lee ya yi magana sosai game da batun yin amfani da Intane a hanyar da ta dace.
A lokacin da aka kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee ya ci gaba da zama Founder da kuma Shugaba na Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, da Web Foundation da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina da bege mai girma game da wannan sabon zamani na Intanet", in ji Berners-Lee.
