Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar wasan, kamar yadda yake yi a dukan wasansa a Amirka, wannan ɗan wasa mai nasara sau bakwai ya raba ranarsa tsakanin samun yabo da kuma yin aiki don ya magance matsalolin da ke damunsa.
