Idan tsayin filin wasa ba zai zama matsala ba, Mickelson, a wasansa na tara a ranar Lahadi, zai yi adawa da dan wasan Birtaniya mai suna Francesco Molinari, wanda ya yi aiki tare da mai wasan Tommy Fleetwood don lashe wasanni hudu a wannan makon.
