A lokacin rani, zafin rana yana sa waɗannan gidajen abinci na Biritaniya su yi aiki fiye da gidajen abinci.
Kasuwancin ƙwari ya ragu da kashi 2.7 cikin ɗari a watan Yuli - amma yanayin ya yi muni a yankunan da suka bunƙasa inda ya ragu da kashi 4.8 cikin ɗari, in ji ƙididdigar.
Peter Martin, wani mai ba da shawara a kan kasuwanci a CGA, wanda ya tara waɗannan alkaluman ya ce: "Cikin zafi da kuma yawan masu halarta a gasar cin kofin duniya a Ingila, watan Yuli ya bi misalin watan Yuni, inda farashin kaya ya tashi da kashi 2.8 bisa ɗari, sai dai kuma an rage yawan wuraren da ake yin wasannin.
