Ɗaya cikin yara biyar - wasu a ƙarƙashin shekara 11 - suna yin asusun sirri da ba a gaya wa manya ba.
Wani bincike da aka yi a kan ɗaliban makarantar sakandare 20,000 ya nuna cewa akwai "shafin Instagram na ƙarya" da yawa - wato, dandalin da ake amfani da shi wajen saka hotuna.
Wannan labarin ya sa na damu cewa wataƙila abin da ke cikin waɗannan shafukan yana da lahani.
Kashi 20 cikin ɗari na ɗaliban sun ce suna amfani da babban asusun ajiya mai tsabta da za su nuna wa iyayensu, kuma suna da asusun ajiya na biyu.
Wani mahaifi da ya sami asusun sirri na 'yarsa mai shekara 13 ya gano cewa tana matsa wa wasu su "ƙara yin lalata da ita".
Binciken, wanda Digital Awareness UK da kuma Headmasters and Headmistresses Conference (HMC) na makarantun masu zaman kansu suka gudanar, ya gano cewa kashi 40 cikin dari na yara masu shekaru 11 zuwa 18 suna da bayanan martaba guda biyu, kuma rabin yara sun ce suna da asusun sirri.
"Abin baƙin ciki, matasa suna fuskantar jarabar kafa dandalin Intane da iyayensu da malamansu ba za su iya gani ba", in ji Mike Buchanan, shugaban hukumar HMC.
Eilidh Doyle zai zama "muryar 'yan wasa" a hukumar 'yan wasa ta Scotland
An zaɓi Eilidh Doyle ya zama memba na hukumar kula da wasan motsa jiki ta Scotland a matsayin shugaban da ba a naɗa ba a babban taron shekara-shekara na ƙungiyar.
Doyle tana ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasan Scotland da suka fi samun nasara a wasan tsere kuma shugabanta Ian Beattie ya bayyana wannan matsayin a matsayin babbar dama ga masu gudanar da wasan don amfana daga tarin ilimin da yarinyar ta tara a duniya a cikin shekaru goma da suka gabata.
"Eilidh yana da daraja a Scotland, Birtaniya da kuma duniya ta hanyar masu tsere kuma muna fatan cewa tsere a Scotland ya amfana da shi a cikin kwamiti", in ji Beattie.
Doyle ya ce: "Na shirya in zama muryar tseren kuma ina fatan in ƙara ƙarfin da nake da shi na taimaka wajen gudanar da wasan a Scotland".
Wannan 'yar Amirka, wadda ta lashe zinare a tseren mita 200 da 400 a gasar Olympics ta 1996 a Atlanta kuma ta yi magana da BBC, ta zama marar iya tafiya bayan da ta yi ciwon shanyewar jiki.
