Girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Mutane 384 ne girgizar kasa da kuma guguwar da ta afkawa garin Palau a ranar Juma'a ta kashe, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai haura sama.
Sa'ad da aka fasa tattaunawa, masu kawo agaji ba su samu isashen saƙo daga Donggala ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palu da ke kusa da wurin da girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku.
A Palu, mutane 16,000 ne suka mutu a lokacin da wannan bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda ke da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da aka yi girgizar ƙasa da kuma ambaliyar ruwa, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da samun 'yanci.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan mil 300 (180 miles) a gaɓar teku a gabashin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Wannan yanki da ke da ofisoshin gwamnati na lardin yana da mazauna 299,200 a shekara ta 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala.
Ana kuma haƙa dutse mai daraja Nickel a wannan lardin, amma an fi samun dutse mai daraja a Morowali, a wata gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami sun addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, guguwa ta halaka mutane 200 kuma ta halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Ƙari ga haka, a shekara ta 1996, guguwa ta halaka dutsen Donggala, kuma mutane tara sun mutu.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana fuskantar yawan girgizar ƙasa.
Ga jerin manyan girgizar ƙasa da kuma tsunami da aka yi a shekarun baya:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a bakin tekun lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra ta haddasa tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a tekun Indiya, yawancinsu a yankin Aceh.
2005: An yi wata guguwa mai tsanani a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Oktoba da farkon Satumba.
An kashe mutane da yawa a tsibirin Nias, da ke gaɓar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi girma a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta jawo ambaliyar ruwa a gaɓar teku ta kudu, ta kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
An kashe mutane kusan 1,100.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai da ke bakin tekun Sumatra, kuma ta jawo raƙuman ruwa masu tsawon kafa 10.
2016: Wani ƙaramin girgizar ƙasa ya auku a yankin Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh, kuma hakan ya jawo bala'i da damuwa a lokacin da ake tunawa da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a shekara ta 2004.
Babu guguwa da ta taso a lokacin, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-ginen.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 9 da ya yi a Lombok, babban birnin Indonesia, ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata gidaje da yawa kuma ta bar dubban baƙi ba tare da gida ba.
An Kama Sarah Palin, 'Yar Farko a Kan Laifin Zalunci da Tsanantawa
Track Palin, ɗan tsohon Gwamnan Alaska kuma ɗan takarar mataimakin shugaban ƙasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi da laifin ta'addanci
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin yin amfani da mugunta, da yin amfani da makamai masu linzami don hana kama mutane, in ji rahotanni da Alaska State Troopers suka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
A cewar 'yan sanda, sa'ad da wata yarinya da ta gan ta ta nemi ta kira 'yan sanda, Palin ta kwace wayar daga hannunta.
A halin yanzu ana tsare da Palin a gidan yari a Mat-Su Pretrial Facility kuma an saka ta a kan belin da ba shi da lafiya na $500, in ji KTUU.
A ranar Asabar, ya bayyana a gaban kotu, inda ya ce ba shi da laifi, amma ya ce gaskiya ne.
Palin tana da laifuffuka uku na Class A, wanda zai iya jawo hukuncin shekara ɗaya a kurkuku da kuma tara dala 250,000.
Na kuma sami wani laifi na Class B misdemeanour, wanda ake yi da ranar ɗaurin kurkuku da kuma tara har dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shi ne lokaci na farko da aka kama Palin da laifin aikata laifi ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an zarge shi da cutar da mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarta, Sarah Palin, ta gaya wa 'yan sanda game da hatsarin.
Yanzu haka, ana ɗaukaka wannan batun a Kotun Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016 an same shi da laifin yin amfani da tashin hankali, da yin amfani da makamai masu linzami, da kuma gano makami yayin da yake cikin maye a lokacin da ya faru.
Wata budurwarsa ta ce ta buge shi da kofi a fuskarsa.
Sarah Palin ta fuskanci mummunan harin da kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji suka kai a shekarar 2016 bayan da ta danganta tashin hankalin danta da PTSD daga aikinsa a Iraki.
Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia: daruruwan mutane sun mutu
