Masu gabatar da kara a kotu sun bukaci a yanke wa wanda ake zargi da kai harin NYC hukuncin kisa
Masu gabatar da kara a birnin New York sun bukaci a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da kai hari a birnin New York City da ya kashe mutane takwas -- shari'a da ba a taɓa yi ba a ƙasar domin shari'ar da ta shafi dukan duniya tun daga shekara ta 1953.
Ana zargin Saipov, ɗan shekara 30, da yin amfani da motar Home Depot wajen yin wannan hatsarin a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, yana cin mutan da ke kan kekuna a lokacin bazara.
Don a yanke masa hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara suna bukatar su tabbatar cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "a wurin" kuma ya yi wa mutane rauni a "wurin", in ji sanarwar neman hukuncin kisa da aka yi a Kudancin Birnin New York.
A duka biyun, hukuncin kisa ne, bisa ga dokar kotu.
Makonni bayan hatsarin, wani kotu ya tuhumi Saipov da laifuffuka 22 da suka hada da kisa takwas da taimakon wani mai laifi, wanda ake amfani da shi a kotun da ke kula da shari'ar da ba ta da laifi, da kuma lalata motoci.
Wannan harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi tun da wuri", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna kwatanta halin Saipov da "zafin hali, rashin tausayi da kuma na mata".
"Saffron Habibullaevic Saipov ya jawo wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco ciwo, baƙin ciki, da kuma rashin abokai", in ji sanarwar.
Mutane biyar daga cikin waɗanda aka gayyata sun zo daga ƙasar Ajantina.
Shekara goma ke nan tun lokacin da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a Kudancin New York.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa a lokacin, amma an canja hukuncinsa zuwa rai da rai a kurkuku a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009.
A shekara ta 1953 ne aka yi hukuncin kisa na ƙarshe a New York a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa a kan ƙulla su yi leƙen asiri ga ƙasar Soviet a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe Rosenberg da kuma matarsa a kujerun lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wani ɗan Uzbekistan, bai nuna cewa ya tuba ba daga abin da ya yi a watanni da suka biyo bayan harin, in ji takardun kotu.
Ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa ya yi farin ciki sosai da abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaida wa masu gabatar da kara cewa ya yi wannan harin ne bayan da ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar takardun shari'a.
Har ma ya nemi a saka masa tutar ISIS a ɗakinsa na asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
Mutumin ya musanta dukan tuhume-tuhume 22 da aka yi masa.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin lauyoyin Saipov, ya ce "ba su yi farin ciki ba" da hukuncin da aka yanke wa Saipov.
"Mun yi tunanin cewa zaɓan hukuncin kisa maimakon hukuncin kisa zai ƙara wa waɗanda aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa wahala", in ji Paton.
Da farko lauyoyin Saipov sun nemi lauyoyin gwamnati su hana su yanke masa hukuncin kisa.
'Yan majalisar dokokin Tory sun ce ya kamata a baiwa NIGEL FARAGE aikin kula da tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ne ya yi alkawarin 'tattara jama'a' a yau a lokacin da ake ta gunaguni a majalisun Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa 'sun ji tsoron' masu shakka game da Turai - kamar yadda wani dan majalisa Theresa May ya yi wa kansa alkawarin kasancewa a gaban tattaunawar da aka yi da kungiyar EU.
Shugaban jam'iyyar Conservative mai zaman kansa Peter Bone ya yi wannan jawabi a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta 'fita' yanzu idan Farage ne Sakataren Brexit.
Amma matsalar da ke tsakanin Mama May da kuma jam'iyyarta ta kara tsanantawa yayin da 'yan Tories masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a cikin birnin ke gudanar da zanga-zangar neman ficewar kasar daga yarjejeniyar.
Ana kuma matsa wa babban shugaban kasar da ya ci gaba da kula da kungiyarsa a yayin da ake fuskantar hare-hare daga bangarorin Brexit, Remain da kuma EU.
Abokan hulɗarsu sun ce suna ci gaba da ƙoƙarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da yiwuwar rashin daidaituwa - tilasta wa masu shakka game da Euro da Labour su zabi tsakanin abin da suke da shi da 'ruhu'.
Bone ya gaya wa taron Leave Means Leave da ke Solihull cewa yana son ya 'bar Chequers.'
Ya ce za a naɗa Farage a matsayin ɗan majalisa kuma a ba shi aikin tuntuɓar Brussels.
'Wadanda suka riga sun shiga aikin, yanzu sun riga sun fita,' in ji su.
'Zan yi hamayya da Brexit amma dole ne mu bar tsarin Chequers,' in ji wani ɗan majalisa daga Wellingborough.
Da yake magana game da ƙin EU, ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙi don mu sami iko ba.
Muna son mu kafa wa kanmu dokoki da ƙa'idodi kamar yadda al'umma take yi.'
Bone ya musanta cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun bayan zaben 2016: 'Ra'ayin cewa ra'ayin Birtaniya ya canza kuma yana son zama ba daidai ba ne.'
Wani ɗan majalisa mai suna Andrea Jenkyns, wanda ya goyi bayan 'yan majalisa a lokacin taron, ya gaya wa manema labarai cewa: 'Ina gaya muku: Ya firaministan ƙasa, ku saurari jama'a.
'Mafi yawan 'yan ƙasa ba su san da Chequers ba, 'yan adawa ba za su amince da shi ba, jam'iyyarmu ba ta san da shi ba kuma ba ta san da masu magana da yawunmu da suke zuwa kan tituna don su yi mana barazana a wurarenmu ba.
Don Allah ku saurari jawabin Chequers.'
A wata sanarwa da ta yi wa May, ta ce: 'Ma'aikatan gwamnati da yawa suna jinkirin cika alkawuransu.'
Farage ya gaya wa 'yan siyasa da ke wurin cewa suna bukatar su "ji haushi" idan suna son su yi watsi da zaɓen da aka yi a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
'Wannan batu yanzu batun imani ne tsakanin mu - mutane - da kuma 'yan siyasa,' in ji su.
'Sun yi kokarin rikita batun Brexit kuma mun zo nan yau don gaya musu cewa ba za mu bari su yi hakan ba kuma ba za mu bar su ba'
A wani jawabi da ya yi wa jama'a da suka yi farin ciki, ya daɗa cewa: 'Ina son ku sa 'yan siyasa su yi fushi domin suna so su ɓata batun Brexit.
'Za mu hada kan al'ummar kasar nan da suka ba mu nasarar Brexit kuma ba za mu yi kasa a gwiwa ba har sai mun zama 'yanci, mulkin mallaka, da kuma girman kai a Birtaniya.'
A wani ɓangare kuma, 'Yan Rukunin sun yi tafiya zuwa Birmingham don su yi taron na awa biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Wasu 'yan adawa da Brexit sun rataye wata alama mai suna Tories Against Brexit bayan da aka fara taron a karshen makon nan.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour mai suna Adonis ya yi wa 'yan majalisa ba'a game da rigakafin da suka yi a kan wani katako bayan an buɗe taron.
'Waɗannan mutane ne ke gaya mana cewa za su iya samun manyan cibiyoyin IT da fasahar Kanada da duk hanyoyin sadarwa, kan iyaka mara iyaka, kasuwanci mai sauƙi ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland,' in ji shi.
'Rashin tsari zai zama gama gari'
Babu wani abu da zai iya zama mafi kyau fiye da kyakkyawar Brexit,' in ji shi.
"Warren yana shirin auna a kan neman shugabancin kasar".
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta "tunani batun tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa" bayan zaɓen da aka yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ce wani ɗan majalisa a Massachusetts ya bayyana makasudinsa na nan gaba a wani taron siyasa a wani babban gida a gabashin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, wanda ya yi ta sukar shugaban kasa Donald Trump, yana neman sake zaben a watan Nuwamba a gaban GOP dan majalisa Geoff Diehl, wanda ya zama mataimakin shugaban kasa a zaben 2016 na Trump a Massachusetts.
