Ƙungiyar Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallo biyu a wasan Giants da Dundee
Dundee Stars ta rama rashin nasarar da ta samu a wasan Elite League da Belfast Giants ranar Juma'a ta hanyar lashe wasan da aka buga 5-3 a Dundee ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci kwallo biyu da sauri ta hannun Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun ci gaba da cin kwallaye kafin Dwyer ya sake komawa gaban Giants.
Francois Bouchard ne ya kawo ƙarshen wasan da Dundee ta yi da ta ci kwallo biyu na Lukas Lundvald Nielsen.
Wannan ne wasa na uku a gasar Elite League a wannan kakar da Adam Keefe ya buga, inda ya tashi daga baya ya doke Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a da daddare.
Wannan ne karo na huɗu da waɗannan kungiyoyin suka haɗu a wannan kakar, kuma Giants sun ci wasanninsu uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya ci gaba da buga kwallo a minti na huɗu da 3:35 daga taimakon Kendall McFaull, kuma David Rutherford ya ci gaba da taimakawa lokacin da Beauvillier ya ci gaba da ci gaba da minti kaɗan.
A lokacin da aka fara wasan, Sullivan ya dawo da tawagarsa a wasan da karfe 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya yi wa Cownie kwallo a karfe 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun ci gaba a cikin rabin lokaci lokacin da ya buga kwallo ta biyu a daren a ƙarshen wasa na farko.
Da yake masu sauraro suna taruwa, Bouchard ya sake buga wasan da ya yi daidai da na wasan tseren da ya yi a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun yi aiki tare don taimakawa Nielsen ta ba Dundee damar samun nasara a karo na biyu kuma ta tabbatar da nasarar da ta samu a karo na biyar ta hanyar wasan karshe.
Giants, da suka ci wasanni huɗu cikin biyar, za su yi wasa da Milton Keynes a wasansu na gaba a ranar Jumma'a.
Wani Mai Kula da Jiragen Sama Ya Mutu Domin Ya Taimaki Dubban Mutane Su Tsira
