Alamar Red Tide: Ƙarancin Tide a Pinellas, Manatee, da Sarasota
Wani sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kifi da Dawa da ke Florida ya nuna cewa an samu raguwar adadin Red Tide a wasu yankunan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an samu raguwar yawan masu kamuwa da cutar a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier - wanda ke nuna cewa an samu raguwa.
Ruwan Tekun Ƙasa yana tafiya mil 130 daga bakin teku zuwa kudu maso yamma a Pinellas County zuwa kudu maso kudu a Lee County.
Ana iya samun filin wasa da ke da nisan mil shida daga iyakar Hillsborough County, amma ya yi ƙasa da na wannan makon.
An kuma ga Red Tide a Pasco County.
An ba da rahoton mafi yawan abubuwan da aka samu a cikin Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, an fara samun su a cikin yankin Hillsborough County, an ba da rahoton mafi yawan abubuwan da aka samu a Manatee County, a cikin yankin Sarasota County, an ba da rahoton mafi ƙarancin abubuwan da aka samu a Charlotte County, an ba da rahoton mafi yawan abubuwan da aka samu a bakin teku ko a cikin Lee County, kuma an ba da rahoton mafi ƙarancin abubuwan da aka samu a cikin Collier County.
An ba da rahoto game da haɗari a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma Collier counties.
Ba a samu rahoton wani haɗari da ya faru a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makon da ya gabata.
